meta {
  name: List all themes
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/brands/{{brandId}}/themes
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Lists all the themes in your brand.

> **Important:** Currently each org supports only one theme, therefore this contains a single object only.

**Responses:**
- `200`: Successfully returned the list of themes
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
